item.title: TJR2489_Project2_Sp2021 - Modeling, Testing, and Prediction
item.description: Building Prediction and Estimate Models for EA Sports’ FIFA 21 Soccer Players Introduction to FIFA21 and FutBin Data The latest addition of EA Sports’ worldwide hit video game is FIFA 21, released on October 6th, 2020. FIFA allows users to play with their favorite soccer stars in a fast-paced football (soccer) simulation which tests users IQ, reactions, and decision making skills through the course of a game (12-15 real minutes).
